I could list a hundred and one excuses why this is a bad run, but I won't... much.

- Got 6(!) crit chips, and panicked when I saw them all in my menu so I wasted a bunch of time there.
- Messed up all the easy skips and got the hard ones no problem.
- I'm still going fangless because I don't see what the Fang really does for you i the current route.
- Cores 1 should've been 10 seconds faster! I had so much damage and just input the wrong attack 3 times in a row.
- Eve phase 1 went fine and tried to mix it up with a more Gatling focus during phase 2, the dps is definitely higher if you can stay up on him.
- My prologue was VERY bad. Messed up the initial clip for lava skip of all things twice! And Engels pops his missile move right before the trigger to begin the final punch sequence.
